title: 2006/09/14-15 - The Calm Before The Storm - WOXY.com
description:

before their final broadcast, hence the name "The Calm Before The Storm".
These start at the end of Shiv&#039;s set on the 14th and continue until the 
beginning of Barb&#039;s set on the 15th.
